{"tid":1782923,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"對於近日網上流傳李嘉先生為本公司董事之一","createTime":"2019-12-14T11:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T10:11:05.000Z","uid":104804,"like":431,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"abb3c445dde9f36c2c1851dbbb8e0c07b6f2091b","tid":1782923,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"本公司鄭重聲明，於2018年初因李嘉先生和本店股東理念差異而被辭退，而李嘉先生並沒持有本公司任何股份，他和本公司無任何關係，故此其一切私人行為均不代表本公司立場。<br />\n無故因李嘉先生個人行為牽涉其中，甚感無奈。<br />\n<br />\n古早味由始至終由台灣人經營，小店形式經營台灣傳統菜。<br />\n<br />\n古早味不持有任何政治立場，一直堅持專注推廣傳統台灣菜，黃藍是政見，黑白是良知，特此鄭重聲明<br />\n<br />\n以免誤會，歡迎去公司註冊處查閱本店股權，謝謝🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />割得好反正我都未食過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇李嘉都係藍既啦罷食"},{"pid":"2459110bfef326005780741c10c02fca96a524dc","tid":1782923,"uid":251769,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請各位喺出post前都再貼一張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCCpQSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCCpQSW.jpg&h=7105947f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8478cfad5609d90b92350e64e936775ad3fc022","tid":1782923,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"73af15b597e858eff2503c806ee1522fc2040cac","tid":1782923,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T